Bastion Hosts:
=============

    - Bastion host is located in the Public Subnet which has internet access
    - Connect to EC2 instances using SSH
    - You then use the Bastion Host to initate an SSH/RDP session over the private Subnet
    - Safely admin EC2 instances without exposing to the internet


    Exam Tips:
    ==========

    - Bastion is a host that is connected to a Public Subnet
    - Connect over internet
    - Securely connect instances in a private Subnet
    - Allows you to safely administer your EC2 instances without exposing them to internet
    - Incoming SSH/RDP instances

    
        


